@startuml
title Vote & Moderate Review - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Pet Owner" as Owner
actor "Receptionist/Admin" as Staff
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "reviews-service\nReviewController" as ReviewController
participant "ReviewModerationController" as ModerationController
participant "ReviewService" as Service
database "reviews schema" as DB

Owner -> Web: Click helpful / not helpful
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/reviews/{id}/votes
Gateway -> ReviewController: route with USER JWT
ReviewController -> Service: vote(reviewId, voteType, user)
Service -> DB: upsert ReviewVote and update helpfulCount
ReviewController --> Web: ReviewResponse

Staff -> Web: Open moderation queue
Web -> Gateway: PATCH /api/v1/reviews/{id}/moderation
Gateway -> ModerationController: route with STAFF/ADMIN
ModerationController -> Service: approve/hide/delete(reviewId)
Service -> DB: transition ReviewStatus
ModerationController --> Web: moderated ReviewResponse
@enduml
